55.2	Adventure_(Atari_2600)	Adventure (Atari 2600)	Adventure is a 1979 video game for the Atari 2600 video game console and is considered the first action-adventure game. Its creator, Warren Robinett, introduced the first widely-known Easter egg to the gaming world.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/60/Adventure_Box_Front.jpg/200px-Adventure_Box_Front.jpg
